data.description: Check out this lovely 2 story home located in the desirable River Vally Highlands subdivision.  This Pulte built home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, Living room, family room and sunroom.  The kitchen offers an eat in space and a full complement of kitchen appliances.  Upstairs you will find a loft that can be finished for another bedroom.  The finished lower level can be used as a bedroom.  Enjoy the back patio as it overlooks green space.  Very close to 33, shopping and restaurants.
